desc: We found a small scout ship which could aid in your mission, but it is a RoboCorpIntergalactic product, and requires a serial number before you can use it. This serial verifier looks a lot like the one our robot used, but now the serial number needs to be 20 digits. Can you take a look and find a valid serial number?
hint: They still teach you to solve systems of equations in math classes, right?
